title: Clownelia Street Theory- SwiftTok Detective Debunks Karma!
description:
The SwiftTok Detective, Hannah, joins us on Clownelia Street to talk all the rumors, all the theories, and which re-recording is next!
Check out Hannah on TikTok- SwiftTokDetective. Listen to her music on Spotify, Huhahnuh.
